title: Can Google take my content off other websites?
content: A website known mp3.racha.top had my speedpaint from YouTube. I looked up "awkwardish furry dice boi" and the video was actually on this website. This website never emailed me or contacted me about using my content and they don't seem to have any way to contact them. Part of it is also some foreign language I am unfamiliar with. What can I do?
